\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:adv_CS"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

 we obtain the complete discrete form
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\theta_{i}^{n+1}-\theta_{i}^{n}}{\Delta t}=-c\frac{\theta_{i+1}^{n}-\theta_{i-1}^{n}}{2\Delta x}
\]

