\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard

\size footnotesize
By rearranging the numerical solution of the FTCS scheme
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\theta_{i}^{n+1}=\theta_{i}^{n}-c\frac{\theta_{i+1}^{n}-\theta_{i-1}^{n}}{2\Delta x}\Delta t
