 the Courant number:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\theta_{i}^{n+1}=\theta_{i}^{n}-\mathcal{C}\left(\theta_{i}^{n}-\theta_{i-1}^{n}\right);\ \theta_{i}^{n+1}=\theta_{i}^{n}-\mathcal{C}\left(\theta_{i+1}^{n}-\theta_{i}^{n}\right)
